title: Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP wins the Marconi Award for Personality of the Year. Peter Schrager of Good Morning Football tells us what he thinks is the No.1  storyline of the NFL season. And Hall of Famer Joe Dumars shares Michael Jordan stories from his playing days.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
